Of Cabbages and Kings is the eponymously titled EP by Of Cabbages and Kings, released by Purge/Sound League on 1987.

* John Erskine – vocals (B)
* Frank Settembrini – bass guitar (A2)

* Eleanor Kostyk – illustrations
